        "TileImage": "$($repository 43d17717-5d65-41d0-bc38-7b0bc7503469).Image",
        "Description": "Have you ever looked at a Hitman NPC and thought: &quot;Man, how I would massacre you if only you weren&apos;t a non target...&quot;? Well then you&apos;ve come to the right place pal! In this contract series I will pick out the most infuriating NPCs in each mission so that you can kill them without regret :)\r\rGoddamn this map is great. My second favorite in the entire WOA Trilogy. Allan Guzman is the only genuinely annoying NPC, other than that this map rocks.",
